- `getFromApi()` - GET requests
- `combineHeaders()` - Merge header objects

### Response Handling
- `createJsonResponseHandler()` - Parse JSON responses
- `createBinaryResponseHandler()` - Handle binary image data
- `createJsonErrorResponseHandler()` - Parse error responses
- `createStatusCodeErrorResponseHandler()` - Handle HTTP status errors

### Configuration
- `loadApiKey()` - Load API key from parameter or environment variable
- `loadSetting()` - Load any string setting from parameter or environment
- `loadOptionalSetting()` - Load optional settings

### Image Processing
- `convertImageModelFileToDataUri()` - Convert image files to data URIs
- `downloadBlob()` - Download image from URL

### Headers & Utilities
- `withUserAgentSuffix()` - Add user agent to headers
- `withoutTrailingSlash()` - Clean up URLs
- `resolve()` - Handle resolvable types (sync/async values)
- `parseProviderOptions()` - Parse provider-specific options

